# PMM AI Agent Instructions — Cursor Entry Point

Read AGENTS.md at the repository root for the complete PMM development guide, including product overview, architecture, domain model, tech stack, and global conventions.

## Component Guides

When working on a specific component, read the relevant guide:

- managed/** → .github/instructions/managed.instructions.md (pmm-managed server backend)
- agent/** → .github/instructions/agent.instructions.md (pmm-agent client agent)
- admin/** → .github/instructions/admin.instructions.md (pmm-admin CLI)
- api/** → .github/instructions/api.instructions.md (Protobuf API definitions)
- qan-api2/** → .github/instructions/qan-api2.instructions.md (Query Analytics API)
- vmproxy/** → .github/instructions/vmproxy.instructions.md (VictoriaMetrics proxy)
- ui/** → .github/instructions/ui.instructions.md (React frontend)
- api-tests/** → .github/instructions/api-tests.instructions.md (API integration tests)
- build/** → .github/instructions/build.instructions.md (Build and packaging)
